msgid "List customer messages"
msgstr "Daftar pesan pelanggan"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get a paginated list of customer messages from all sources.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    **Sources:**\n"
"    - `contact_form`: Messages from contact form submissions\n"
"    - `order_note`: Customer notes attached to orders\n"
"\n"
"    Messages are sorted by newest first by default.\n"
"\n"
"    **Deep Linking:**\n"
"    - For `source='contact_form'`: Use `message_id` to navigate to message "
"detail\n"
"    - For `source='order_note'`: Use `order_number` to navigate to order "
"detail\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan daftar berhalaman dari pesan pelanggan dari semua sumber.\n"
"\n"
"**Batasi Permintaan:** 300 permintaan per menit\n"
"\n"
"**Sumber:**\n"
"- `contact_form`: Pesan dari pengiriman formulir kontak\n"
"- `order_note`: Catatan pelanggan yang terlampir ke pesanan\n"
"\n"
"Pesan diurutkan berdasarkan terbaru terlebih dahulu secara default.\n"
"\n"
"**Tautan Mendalam:**\n"
"- Untuk `source='contact_form'`: Gunakan `message_id` untuk beralih ke "
"detail pesan\n"
"- Untuk `source='order_note'`: Gunakan `order_number` untuk beralih ke "
"detail pesanan\n"
"    "

msgid "Filter by source: 'all', 'contact_form', 'order_note'"
msgstr "Saring berdasarkan sumber: 'all', 'contact_form', 'order_note'"

msgid "Filter by status: 'all', 'unread', 'read', 'replied', 'archived'"
msgstr ""
"Saring berdasarkan status: 'all', 'unread', 'read', 'replied', 'archived'"

msgid "Search by sender name, email, or subject"
msgstr "Cari berdasarkan nama pengirim, email, atau subjek"

msgid "Get message details"
msgstr "Dapatkan detail pesan"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get full details of a customer message.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    **URL Format:** `/messages/{source}/{id}/`\n"
"    - `source`: Either 'contact_form' or 'order_note'\n"
"    - `id`: The message ID within that source\n"
"\n"
"    Automatically marks the message as read if it was unread.\n"
"\n"
"    **Deep Linking:**\n"
"    - For `source='contact_form'`: Returns full contact form message\n"
"    - For `source='order_note'`: Returns order note with order info for "
"linking\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan detail lengkap dari pesan pelanggan.\n"
"\n"
"**Batasi Permintaan:** 300 permintaan per menit\n"
"\n"
"**Format URL:** `/messages/{source}/{id}/`\n"
"- `source`: Either 'contact_form' atau 'order_note'\n"
"- `id`: ID pesan dalam sumber tersebut\n"
"\n"
"Secara otomatis menandai pesan sebagai telah dibaca jika sebelumnya belum "
"dibaca.\n"
"\n"
"**Tautan Mendalam:**\n"
"- Untuk `source='contact_form'`: Mengembalikan pesan formulir kontak "
"lengkap\n"
"- Untuk `source='order_note'`: Mengembalikan catatan pesanan dengan "
"informasi pesanan untuk penautan\n"
"    "

msgid "Message not found."
msgstr "Pesan tidak ditemukan."

msgid "Invalid source. Must be \"contact_form\" or \"order_note\"."
msgstr ""
"Sumber tidak valid. Harus menjadi \"contact_form\" atau \"order_note\"."

msgid "Update message status"
msgstr "Perbarui status pesan"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Update the status of a customer message.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    **URL Format:** `/messages/{source}/{id}/status/`\n"
"    - `source`: Either 'contact_form' or 'order_note'\n"
"    - `id`: The message ID within that source\n"
"\n"
"    **Status Options:**\n"
"    - read: Mark as read\n"
"    - replied: Mark as replied (contact_form only)\n"
"    - archived: Archive the message (contact_form only)\n"
"\n"
"    Note: OrderNotes only support 'read' status.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Perbarui status pesan pelanggan.\n"
"\n"
"**Batas Permintaan:** 300 permintaan per menit\n"
"\n"
"**Format URL:** `/messages/{source}/{id}/status/`\n"
"- `source`: Either 'contact_form' atau 'order_note'\n"
"- `id`: ID pesan dalam sumber tersebut\n"
"\n"
"**Opsi Status:**\n"
"- read: Tandai sebagai dibaca\n"
"- replied: Tandai sebagai dibalas (hanya untuk contact_form)\n"
"- archived: Arsipkan pesan (hanya untuk contact_form)\n"
"\n"
"Catatan: OrderNotes hanya mendukung status 'read'.\n"
"    "

msgid "Invalid status update."
msgstr "Pembaruan status tidak valid."

msgid "Order notes only support \"read\" status."
msgstr "Catatan pesanan hanya mendukung status \"read\"."

msgid "Message status updated successfully."
msgstr "Status pesan telah diperbarui dengan sukses."

msgid "Get unread message count"
msgstr "Dapatkan jumlah pesan belum dibaca"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get the count of unread customer messages from all sources.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    Useful for badge display in the app.\n"
"\n"
"    Returns breakdown by source:\n"
"    - `contact_form`: Unread contact form submissions\n"
"    - `order_note`: Unread customer notes on orders\n"
"    - `total`: Combined total\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan jumlah pesan pelanggan yang belum dibaca dari semua sumber.\n"
"\n"
"**Batas Permintaan:** 300 permintaan per menit\n"
"\n"
"Berguna untuk tampilan badge di aplikasi.\n"
"\n"
"Mengembalikan breakdown berdasarkan sumber:\n"
"- `contact_form`: Pesan formulir kontak yang belum dibaca\n"
"- `order_note`: Catatan pelanggan pada pesanan yang belum dibaca\n"
"- `total`: Total keseluruhan\n"
"    "

msgid "Get message counts by status"
msgstr "Dapatkan jumlah pesan berdasarkan status"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get count of messages by status and source for badge display.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    Returns counts for both sources:\n"
"    - `contact_form`: Full status breakdown (unread, read, replied, "
"archived)\n"
"    - `order_note`: Simple status (unread, read)\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan jumlah pesan berdasarkan status dan sumber untuk tampilan "
"badge.\n"
"\n"
"**Batasi Tingkat:** 300 permintaan per menit\n"
"\n"
"Mengembalikan jumlah untuk kedua sumber:\n"
"- `contact_form`: Pemecahan status lengkap (belum dibaca, dibaca, dibalas, "
"diarik)\n"
"- `order_note`: Status sederhana (belum dibaca, dibaca)\n"
"    "

msgid "Reply to customer message"
msgstr "Balas pesan pelanggan"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\n"
"    Reply to a customer message from the contact form.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    **URL Format:** `/messages/contact_form/{id}/reply/`\n"
"\n"
"    This endpoint:\n"
"    1. Stores the reply text against the message\n"
"    2. Updates message status to 'replied'\n"
"    3. Optionally sends an email to the customer\n"
"\n"
"    Note: This endpoint only works for `contact_form` messages.\n"
"    For order notes, use the order notes reply endpoint instead.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Balas pesan dari formulir kontak pelanggan.\n"
"\n"
"**Batas Permintaan:** 300 permintaan per menit\n"
"\n"
"**Format URL:** `/messages/contact_form/{id}/reply/`\n"
"\n"
"Endpoint ini:\n"
"1. Menyimpan teks balasan terhadap pesan\n"
"2. Memperbarui status pesan menjadi 'dibalas'\n"
"3. Secara opsional mengirimkan email ke pelanggan\n"
"\n"
"Catatan: Endpoint ini hanya berfungsi untuk pesan `contact_form`.\n"
"Untuk catatan pesanan, gunakan endpoint balasan catatan pesanan.\n"
"    "

msgid "Invalid reply data."
msgstr "Data balasan tidak valid."

msgid "List orders"
msgstr "Daftar pesanan"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get a paginated list of orders with filtering and sorting.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    **Filtering:**\n"
"    Use either `status` for a specific status or `filter_type` for status "
"groups.\n"
"    If `status` is provided (not 'all'), `filter_type` is ignored.\n"
"\n"
"    **Filter Types (groups):**\n"
"    - all: All orders (default)\n"
"    - open: Orders with status pending or processing\n"
"    - completed: Orders with status shipped or delivered\n"
"    - refunded: Orders with status refunded or cancelled\n"
"\n"
"    **Sort Options:**\n"
"    - -created_at: Newest first (default)\n"
"    - created_at: Oldest first\n"
"    - -total_amount: Highest value first\n"
"    - total_amount: Lowest value first\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan daftar pesanan yang dipaginasi dengan penyaringan dan "
"pengurutan.\n"
"\n"
"**Batas Permintaan:** 300 permintaan per menit\n"
"\n"
"**Penyaringan:**\n"
"Gunakan `status` untuk status tertentu atau `filter_type` untuk kelompok "
"status.\n"
"Jika `status` disediakan (bukan 'semua'), `filter_type` diabaikan.\n"
"\n"
"**Jenis Penyaringan (kelompok):**\n"
"- all: Semua pesanan (default)\n"
"- open: Pesanan dengan status menunggu atau sedang diproses\n"
"- completed: Pesanan dengan status dikirim atau telah sampai\n"
"- refunded: Pesanan dengan status dikembalikan atau dibatalkan\n"
"\n"
"**Opsi Pengurutan:**\n"
"- -created_at: Terbaru terlebih dahulu (default)\n"
"- created_at: Terlama terlebih dahulu\n"
"- -total_amount: Nilai tertinggi terlebih dahulu\n"
"- total_amount: Nilai terendah terlebih dahulu\n"
"    "

msgid ""
"Filter type: 'all', 'open', 'completed', 'refunded'. Ignored if 'status' is "
"provided."
msgstr ""
"Jenis penyaring: 'all', 'open', 'completed', 'refunded'. Diabaikan jika "
"'status' disediakan."

msgid "Specific status filter"
msgstr "Penyaring status spesifik"

msgid "Search by order number, email, customer name, or phone number"
msgstr ""
"Cari berdasarkan nomor pesanan, email, nama pelanggan, atau nomor telepon"

msgid "Sort field"
msgstr "Kolom pengurutan"

msgid "Get order details"
msgstr "Dapatkan detail pesanan"

