msgid "Add note to order"
msgstr "Tambahkan catatan ke pesanan"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Add a note to an order. Can be used to reply to customer messages.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 30 requests per minute (sensitive operation)\n"
"\n"
"    **Fields:**\n"
"    - `note`: The note content (required)\n"
"    - `is_customer_visible`: Whether the customer can see this note "
"(default: true)\n"
"    - `notify_customer`: Whether to send email notification to customer "
"(default: false)\n"
"\n"
"    When replying to a customer's order note, set `is_customer_visible: "
"true` so\n"
"    the customer can see your response in their order history.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Tambahkan catatan ke pesanan. Dapat digunakan untuk membalas pesan "
"pelanggan.\n"
"\n"
"**Batasan Tingkat:** 30 permintaan per menit (operasi sensitif)\n"
"\n"
"**Bidang:**\n"
"- `note`: Isi catatan (wajib)\n"
"- `is_customer_visible`: Apakah pelanggan dapat melihat catatan ini "
"(default: true)\n"
"- `notify_customer`: Apakah akan mengirim notifikasi email ke pelanggan "
"(default: false)\n"
"\n"
"Ketika membalas catatan pesanan pelanggan, atur `is_customer_visible: true` "
"agar\n"
"pelanggan dapat melihat respons Anda dalam riwayat pesanan mereka.\n"
"    "

msgid "Invalid note data."
msgstr "Data catatan tidak valid."

msgid "Note added successfully."
msgstr "Catatan telah ditambahkan dengan sukses."

msgid "Update order status"
msgstr "Perbarui status pesanan"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Update the status of an order.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 30 requests per minute (sensitive operation)\n"
"\n"
"    **Allowed Transitions:**\n"
"    - pending → processing, cancelled\n"
"    - processing → shipped, cancelled, pending\n"
"    - shipped → delivered, processing\n"
"    - delivered → refunded\n"
"    - cancelled → pending (reopen)\n"
"    - refunded → (terminal state)\n"
"\n"
"    Optionally include tracking number when marking as shipped.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Perbarui status pesanan.\n"
"\n"
"**Batasan Tingkat:** 30 permintaan per menit (operasi sensitif)\n"
"\n"
"**Transisi yang Diperbolehkan:**\n"
"- pending → processing, cancelled\n"
"- processing → shipped, cancelled, pending\n"
"- shipped → delivered, processing\n"
"- delivered → refunded\n"
"- cancelled → pending (reopen)\n"
"- refunded → (state terminal)\n"
"\n"
"Opsional, sertakan nomor pelacakan saat menandai sebagai telah dikirim.\n"
"    "

msgid "Order status updated successfully."
msgstr "Status pesanan telah diperbarui dengan sukses."

msgid "Update tracking number"
msgstr "Perbarui nomor pelacakan"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Update or add tracking number for an order.\n"
"\n"
