msgid "List products"
msgstr "Daftar produk"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Get a paginated list of products with filtering and sorting.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"\n"
"    **Stock Status Filter:**\n"
"    - all: All products (default)\n"
"    - in_stock: Products with available stock > low_stock_threshold\n"
"    - low_stock: Products with 0 < available stock <= low_stock_threshold\n"
"    - out_of_stock: Products with available stock <= 0\n"
"\n"
"    **Sort Options (use 'ordering' parameter):**\n"
"    - name: Name A-Z\n"
"    - -name: Name Z-A\n"
"    - -created_at: Newest first\n"
"    - created_at: Oldest first\n"
"    - stock_quantity: Lowest stock first\n"
"    - -stock_quantity: Highest stock first\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan daftar terbatas produk dengan penapisan dan pengurutan.\n"
"\n"
"**Batas Permintaan:** 300 permintaan per menit\n"
"\n"
"**Penapis Status Stok:**\n"
"- all: Semua produk (default)\n"
"- in_stock: Produk dengan stok yang tersedia > low_stock_threshold\n"
"- low_stock: Produk dengan 0 < stok yang tersedia <= low_stock_threshold\n"
"- out_of_stock: Produk dengan stok yang tersedia <= 0\n"
"\n"
"**Opsi Pengurutan (gunakan parameter 'ordering'):**\n"
"- name: Nama A-Z\n"
"- -name: Nama Z-A\n"
"- -created_at: Terbaru dahulu\n"
"- created_at: Terlama dahulu\n"
"- stock_quantity: Stok terendah dahulu\n"
"- -stock_quantity: Stok tertinggi dahulu\n"
"    "

msgid "Filter by product status: 'all', 'draft', 'published', 'discontinued'"
msgstr ""
"Saring berdasarkan status produk: 'semua', 'draf', 'diterbitkan', "
"'dihentikan'"

msgid "Filter by stock status: 'all', 'in_stock', 'low_stock', 'out_of_stock'"
