"    **Rate Limit:** 300 requests per minute\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Dapatkan semua variasi untuk produk tertentu, dengan informasi stok.\n"
"\n"
"**Batas Tingkat:** 300 permintaan per menit\n"
"    "

msgid "Create product variant"
msgstr "Buat variasi produk"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Create a new variant for a product. The product must be of type "
"'variable'.\n"
"    If `initial_stock` is provided and the product tracks inventory, a "
"StockItem\n"
"    is auto-created for the default warehouse.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 30 requests per minute (sensitive operation)\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Buat variasi baru untuk produk. Produk harus bertipe 'variable'.\n"
"Jika `initial_stock` disediakan dan produk melacak inventaris, sebuah "
"StockItem\n"
"akan dibuat otomatis untuk gudang default.\n"
"\n"
"**Batas Tingkat:** 30 permintaan per menit (operasi sensitif)\n"
"    "

#, python-format
msgid ""
"Variants can only be added to variable products. This product is type "
"\"%(type)s\"."
msgstr ""
"Variasi hanya dapat ditambahkan ke produk variabel. Produk ini tipe "
"\"%(type)s\"."

msgid "Invalid variant data."
msgstr "Data variasi tidak valid."

msgid "Variant created successfully."
msgstr "Variasi telah dibuat dengan sukses."

msgid "Update product variant"
msgstr "Perbarui variasi produk"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Partially update a variant. Only provided fields will be changed.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 30 requests per minute (sensitive operation)\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Perbarui sebagian varian. Hanya bidang yang disediakan yang akan "
"diubah.\n"
"\n"
"**Batasi Tingkat:** 30 permintaan per menit (operasi sensitif)\n"
"    "

msgid "Variant not found."
msgstr "Variasi tidak ditemukan."

msgid "Variant updated successfully."
msgstr "Variasi telah diperbarui dengan sukses."

msgid "Delete product variant"
msgstr "Hapus variasi produk"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Permanently delete a variant. Associated StockItems will be cascade-"
"deleted.\n"
"\n"
"    **Rate Limit:** 30 requests per minute (sensitive operation)\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    Hapus permanen varian. StockItems yang terkait akan dihapus secara "
"berantai.\n"
"\n"
"**Batasi Tingkat:** 30 permintaan per menit (operasi sensitif)\n"
"    "

#, python-format
msgid "Variant \"%(name)s\" (%(sku)s) deleted successfully."
msgstr "Variasi \"%(name)s\" (%(sku)s) berhasil dihapus."
